    <item>
      <title>JH 的 Miskin 建议抓住机会拥抱债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-15/take-the-chance-to-embrace-bonds-says-jh-s-miskin-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[约翰汉考克联合首席投资策略师马特·米斯金 (Matt Miskin) 表示，投资者应抓住机会在 2025 年买入债券，因为“好消息对增长来说又是好消息”，因为美国经济并不急于降息。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-15/take-the-chance-to-embrace-bonds-says-jh-s-miskin-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 14:10:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>第六街财团将收购瑞银抵押贷款部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/sixth-street-consortium-said-to-be-buyer-of-ubs-mortgage-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由 Sixth Street Partners 牵头的一组投资者已同意从瑞银集团手中收购瑞士信贷的美国抵押贷款服务业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/sixth-street-consortium-said-to-be-buyer-of-ubs-mortgage-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 14:01:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲信贷交易蓬勃发展，千禧年银行开设新加坡办事处</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/millennium-opens-singapore-office-as-asia-credit-trading-soars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[千禧顾问公司 (Millennium Advisors) 已将其交易和销售业务扩展到亚洲，以利用该地区对电子交易和美元债券日益增长的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/millennium-opens-singapore-office-as-asia-credit-trading-soars</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员们放弃押注美联储大幅降息，因美国经济韧性十足</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/treasury-yields-rise-sharply-as-data-rules-out-big-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国经济强劲反弹促使交易员降低对美联储今年大幅降息的预期，随后美国国债收益率飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/treasury-yields-rise-sharply-as-data-rules-out-big-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 12:51:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国零售销售数据好于预期，新兴市场货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/emerging-market-currencies-hover-around-2-year-high-stocks-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在数据显示美国经济具有韧性之后，发展中国家货币走弱，令对美联储下个月将异常大幅降息的押注降温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/emerging-market-currencies-hover-around-2-year-high-stocks-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:27:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者关注中国经济数据和必和必拓矿场罢工，铜价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/copper-edges-up-as-investors-assess-china-data-mine-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商权衡利空的中国经济数据与全球最大铜矿的劳工中断，铜价连续第二天上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/copper-edges-up-as-investors-assess-china-data-mine-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 03:45:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗紧张局势和美国零售销售强劲推动油价止跌两日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对伊朗可能袭击以色列的担忧和强劲的美国经济数据掩盖了持续的需求担忧，油价在连续两天下跌后走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 23:37:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>零售销售缓解“增长恐慌” 股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/asian-stocks-to-open-weaker-cpi-calms-wall-street-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[零售销售数据凸显了全球最大经济体的实力，导致股市上涨、债市下跌，缓解了人们对美联储高利率可能导致经济明显放缓的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/asian-stocks-to-open-weaker-cpi-calms-wall-street-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 22:36:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
